<div class="legacy-para">
		SENIOR ADMINISTRATION OFFICIAL:&nbsp; Can we just walk through this?&nbsp; Wednesday night, political leadership in New York was given a heads-up.&nbsp; Thursday, the joint intelligence presentation was made to the IAEA by the three intelligence services.</div>
<div class="legacy-para">
