<div class="legacy-para">
		SENIOR ADMINISTRATION OFFICIAL:&nbsp; Thursday afternoon, Vienna time.&nbsp; Today we are sharing, at a technical level, the intelligence about the facility.&nbsp; So we&#39;re going through this very methodically.&nbsp; Obviously the President in the bilateral also gave President Medvedev a heads-up about what we knew.</div>
<div class="legacy-para">
